<title>USA: Acclaim completes credit restructuring.</title>
<headline>Acclaim completes credit restructuring.</headline>
<dateline>GLEN COVE, N.Y. 1997-03-05</dateline>
<text>
<p>Acclaim Entertainment Inc said on Wednesday it completed the restructuring of its domestic credit facilities and is in compliance with new covenants established with two of its lenders.</p>
<p>Those lenders are Bank of New York Co Inc and Fleet Financial Group Inc.</p>
<p>Acclaim also said it has successfully placed a $50 million private offering of 10 percent convertible subordinated notes due 2002.  The notes are convertible into common stock at an initial price of $5.18 per share.</p>
<p>Acclaim publishes computer game software and comic books, among its other business activities.</p>
